## Step Sequence to Follow

When asked to build the full project, follow this order exactly:

1. Scaffold folder structure (both frontend and backend)
2. Set up DB migration scripts
3. Implement auth (backend) → auth (frontend)
4. Implement session creation (backend) → onboarding page (frontend)
5. Implement Normal Revision mode (backend + frontend)
6. Implement PrepRush mode (backend + frontend)
7. Implement Q&A practice (backend + frontend)
8. Implement dashboard page
9. Add loading/error states everywhere
10. Final self-check: trace each user flow end to end

---

## What "Done" Means for Each Task

- Backend endpoint: compiles, handles errors, returns correct DTO shape per PREP_RUSH.md
- Frontend page: renders data, shows loading spinner, shows error message, mobile responsive
- Gemini integration: uses exact prompt from PREP_RUSH.md, parses JSON response, saves to DB

