## Do Not
- Do not use GraphQL — REST only
- Do not use any UI library other than Tailwind CSS (no Material UI, no Chakra)
- Do not use Redux — use React Context + useReducer
- Do not use any ORM other than Spring Data JPA
- Do not change the DB schema defined in PREP_RUSH.md
- Do not add features not described in PREP_RUSH.md without asking
- Do not skip error handling to save time
- Do not hardcode API keys — always read from environment variables
